lly good.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Not the most helpful employees when it comes to assisting customers but both the products I got and the place itself are really good.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Chris L", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/112499116981790578061/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU0a8iJC7boQEd_dCrf5Fmga8i21Z3hDC1bfoNZUfza3RxP4DRB=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-23T17:38:27.535447778Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21Od2R6SjRUa05FZFZOa1JUVmpNVE5yVkVOU01VRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21Od2R6SjRUa05FZFZOa1JUVmpNVE5yVkVOU01VRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2bfe614791fc3:0xf058e2743d614140"}, {"name": "places/ChIJwx95FOa_woARQEFhPXTiWPA/reviews/ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUR0MDRMVDJBRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 years ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "I've heard many times that the staffs are rude, but nope not in my experience! Maybe my dog helped hehe. Anyways always in love with their designs 👍🏻 impressive even", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I've heard many times that the staffs are rude, but nope not in my experience! Maybe my dog helped hehe. Anyways always in love with their designs 👍🏻 impressive even", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "ᄋᄌᄋᄂ", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/114935224022824017343/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL1o1aJH9RgzkSdyonjErckphLDgqeVwNDcg7fPRmttDr-GRJE=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2024-02-06T20:07:05.293385Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUR0MDRMVDJBRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUR0MDRMVDJBRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2bfe614791fc3:0xf058e2743d614140"}, {"name": "places/ChIJwx95FOa_woARQEFhPXTiWPA/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2s5RWFETjJkbmx5WW1OSlIxazRSazE0UlZkRGJtYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a year ago", "rating": 1, "text": {"text": "Jumped in an Uber that cost me short of $30 just to have a look. Wanted to purchase two T-shirts that I liked the look of, I was asked do you want to buy those when I had the two t-shirts in hand. I replied yes, but first I’d like to try them on. And apparently the only policy is no try of T-shirts which seemed convenient, and with the different fits and sizes with palace I thought I can’t just simply buy the shirts so I had to leave them rubbish customer service didn’t do anything to help", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Jumped in an Uber that cost me short of $30 just to have a look. Wanted to purchase two T-shirts that I liked the look of, I was asked do you want to buy those when I had the two t-shirts in hand. I replied yes, but first I’d like to try them on. And apparently the only policy is no try of T-shirts which seemed convenient, and with the different fits and sizes with palace I thought I can’t just simply buy the shirts so I had to leave them rubbish customer service didn’t do anything to help", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Daniel Bramma", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/107323644716673480723/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVyoe78xNJlCH041hqp3CJC7yPNEDdGAxHaL17Vw7uaHWScoBGj=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2025-07-07T00:41:52.097985884Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2s5RWFETjJkbmx5WW1OSlIxazRSazE0UlZkRGJtYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2s5RWFETjJkbmx5WW1OSlIxazRSazE0UlZkRGJtYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2bfe614791fc3:0xf058e2743d614140"